 \frac{a+b}{b+c} + \frac{c+d}{d+a} â‰¤ 4\Big(\frac{a+c}{b+d}\Big) 
a, c \geq 1
b + d\leq 4
 a - \frac {a + b} {b + c} = \frac{ab + ac - a - b} {b + c} = \frac {b(a - 1) + a(c - 1)} {b + c} \geq 0 
 c - \frac{c + d} {d + a} \geq 0 
 \frac {a + b} {b + c} + \frac{c + d} {d + a} \leq a + c \leq \frac 4 {b + d} (a + c) 
